title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA 9am Hour 7/20 - Mike Florio, Dolphins Have It Better?
description: –Nordo fills in for PA, Mike Florio joins to talk all things NFL, Nordo talks some MLB ASG after Buxton’s game winning HR, and he poses the question “Who’s got it better than us?” about the Dolphins.
